    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "Exodus",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 25,
        "summary": "Israel is commanded to donate property and build a tabernacle, the ark of testimony (with the mercy seat and cherubims), a table (for the shewbread), and the candlestick, all according to patterns shown to Moses on the mount.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "And the Lord spake unto Moses, saying,",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Moses 1:2 (1\u20132).",
                        "start": 13,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Speak unto the children of Israel, that they bring me an offering: of every man that giveth it willingly with his heart ye shall take my offering.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 35:4 (4\u20139); D&C 1:38.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 5
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ezra 3:5; 2\u00a0Cor. 8:12; Hel. 6:36; D&C 59:15; 64:34; 97:8. TG\u00a0Initiative.",
                        "start": 95,
                        "end": 104
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And this is the offering which ye shall take of them; gold, and silver, and brass,",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 11
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And blue, and purple, and scarlet, and fine linen, and goats' hair,",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Ne. 13:7 (7\u20138); Ether 10:24.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 8
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 35:23.",
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 49
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 62,
                        "end": 67
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And rams' skins dyed red, and badgers' skins, and shittim wood,",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 26:14.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 9
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0acacia.",
                        "start": 50,
                        "end": 57
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Oil for the light, spices for anointing oil, and for sweet incense,",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 27:20.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 3
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 30:34 (34\u201338).",
                        "start": 19,
                        "end": 25
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 109:35 (35\u201336); 124:39 (38\u201340).",
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 43
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 31:11.",
                        "start": 59,
                        "end": 66
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Onyx stones, and stones to be set in the ephod, and in the breastplate.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 28:9 (6\u201314); Moses 3:12.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 11
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Mosiah 8:10 (10\u201311); D&C 17:1; JS\u2014H 1:35.",
                        "start": 59,
                        "end": 70
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And let them make me a sanctuary; that I may dwell among them.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Temple.",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 32
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Kgs. 6:13; D&C 104:59; 124:27 (26\u201328).",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 50
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [
                    {
                        "class": "iconPointer-OKie_ icon-eLakR icon-ieVZ1",
                        "data-pointer-type": "media",
                        "data-scroll-id": "p8",
                        "title": "Associated Content"
                    }
                ],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "According to all that I shew thee, after the pattern of the tabernacle, and the pattern of all the instruments thereof, even so shall ye make it.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 33:7; D&C 101:23; 124:38 (38\u201341).",
                        "start": 60,
                        "end": 70
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0furniture, equipment, utensils.",
                        "start": 99,
                        "end": 110
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 40
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 142,
                        "end": 145
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And they shall make an ark of shittim wood: two cubits and a half shall be the length thereof, and a cubit and a half the breadth thereof, and a cubit and a half the height thereof.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 35:12; Num. 4:5 (5\u201315); Deut. 10:1; 1\u00a0Sam. 14:18; D&C 85:8.",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 26
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 27,
                        "end": 29
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 66,
                        "end": 74
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt overlay it with pure gold, within and without shalt thou overlay it, and shalt make upon it a crown of gold round about.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt cast four rings of gold for it, and put them in the four corners thereof; and two rings shall be in the one side of it, and two rings in the other side of it.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 55,
                        "end": 59
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 103,
                        "end": 111
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make staves of shittim wood, and overlay them with gold.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 27,
                        "end": 29
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt put the staves into the rings by the sides of the ark, that the ark may be borne with them.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Chr. 15:15.",
                        "start": 65,
                        "end": 68
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The staves shall be in the rings of the ark: they shall not be taken from it.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Kgs. 8:8 (7\u20138).",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 10
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt put into the ark the testimony which I shall give thee.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Kgs. 11:12; Heb. 9:4. TG\u00a0Scriptures, Preservation of.",
                        "start": 36,
                        "end": 45
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make a mercy seat of pure gold: two cubits and a half shall be the length thereof, and a cubit and a half the breadth thereof.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0atonement-cover. Note that it was a golden slab of the same dimension as the top of the ark. A winged cherub was placed on each end. Ex. 37:6 (6\u20139); Heb. 9:5 (4\u20136).",
                        "start": 22,
                        "end": 32
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 33,
                        "end": 35
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 69,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make two cherubims of gold, of beaten work shalt thou make them, in the two ends of the mercy seat.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Art.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 19
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Cherubim.",
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 33
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 36
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 43,
                        "end": 45
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And make one cherub on the one end, and the other cherub on the other end: even of the mercy seat shall ye make the cherubims on the two ends thereof.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0as part of it.",
                        "start": 80,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [
                    {
                        "type": "paper-page-number",
                        "data": 118
                    }
                ],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 75,
                        "end": 79
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And the cherubims shall stretch forth their wings on high, covering the mercy seat with their wings, and their faces shall look one to another; toward the mercy seat shall the faces of the cherubims be.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0they shall face one another (see next line).",
                        "start": 105,
                        "end": 110
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 38,
                        "end": 43
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 117,
                        "end": 127
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt put the mercy seat above upon the ark; and in the ark thou shalt put the testimony that I shall give thee.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 26:34; 30:6 (6\u201310).",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 33
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 16:34; Deut. 31:26; 1\u00a0Kgs. 8:9. TG\u00a0Record Keeping.",
                        "start": 88,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And there I will meet with thee, and I will commune with thee from above the mercy seat, from between the two cherubims which are upon the ark of the testimony, of all things which I will give thee in commandment unto the children of Israel.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 29:43 (32, 43); 30:36 (6, 36); Num. 17:4. TG\u00a0God, Access to; Meetings.",
                        "start": 17,
                        "end": 21
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Lev. 16:2; Num. 1:1; 7:89; Ether 2:14.",
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 51
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Ark of the Covenant.",
                        "start": 77,
                        "end": 87
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Kgs. 19:15.",
                        "start": 110,
                        "end": 119
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 126,
                        "end": 129
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 168,
                        "end": 174
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Thou shalt also make a table of shittim wood: two cubits shall be the length thereof, and a cubit the breadth thereof, and a cubit and a half the height thereof.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 35:13; 37:10 (10\u201316); Heb. 9:2.",
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 28
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 31
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 57,
                        "end": 65
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt overlay it with pure gold, and make thereto a crown of gold round about.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make unto it a border of an hand breadth round about, and thou shalt make a golden crown to the border thereof round about.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make for it four rings of gold, and put the rings in the four corners that are on the four feet thereof.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 90,
                        "end": 93
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Over against the border shall the rings be for places of the staves to bear the table.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make the staves of shittim wood, and overlay them with gold, that the table may be borne with them.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 31,
                        "end": 33
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make the dishes thereof, and spoons thereof, and covers thereof, and bowls thereof, to cover withal: of pure gold shalt thou make them.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Num. 4:7.",
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 30
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0jugs, jars.",
                        "start": 64,
                        "end": 70
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0wherewith to pour libations.",
                        "start": 99,
                        "end": 114
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 116,
                        "end": 118
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt set upon the table shewbread before me alway.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0bread of faces, or bread of the presence. 1\u00a0Kgs. 7:48; Heb. 9:2. TG\u00a0Bread, Shewbread.",
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 43
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make a candlestick of pure gold: of beaten work shall the candlestick be made: his shaft, and his branches, his bowls, his knops, and his flowers, shall be of the same.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 35:14; 37:17 (17\u201324); 1\u00a0Kgs. 7:49; Heb. 9:2; Rev. 1:12.",
                        "start": 22,
                        "end": 33
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0one piece.",
                        "start": 174,
                        "end": 182
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 36
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 48,
                        "end": 50
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And six branches shall come out of the sides of it; three branches of the candlestick out of the one side, and three branches of the candlestick out of the other side:",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Three bowls made like unto almonds, with a knop and a flower in one branch; and three bowls made like almonds in the other branch, with a knop and a flower: so in the six branches that come out of the candlestick.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "IE\u00a0crown-shaped circlets (also vv.\u00a034\u201336).",
                        "start": 41,
                        "end": 42
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0thus shall be the\u00a0\u2026",
                        "start": 157,
                        "end": 166
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 36,
                        "end": 40
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 131,
                        "end": 135
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And in the candlestick shall be four bowls made like unto almonds, with their knops and their flowers.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 23,
                        "end": 31
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 67,
                        "end": 71
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And there shall be a knop under two branches of the same, and a knop under two branches of the same, and a knop under two branches of the same, according to the six branches that proceed out of the candlestick.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Their knops and their branches shall be of the same: all it shall be one beaten work of pure gold.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 60,
                        "end": 68
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 85,
                        "end": 87
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And thou shalt make the seven lamps thereof: and they shall light the lamps thereof, that they may give light over against it.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Num. 8:2 (1\u20134); 1\u00a0Chr. 28:15.",
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 35
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0set up.",
                        "start": 60,
                        "end": 65
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 40:25; Lev. 24:4 (3\u20134).",
                        "start": 70,
                        "end": 75
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And the tongs thereof, and the snuffdishes thereof, shall be of pure gold.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [
                    {
                        "type": "paper-page-number",
                        "data": 119
                    }
                ],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 52,
                        "end": 63
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Of a talent of pure gold shall he make it, with all these vessels.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 2
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "And look that thou make them after their pattern, which was shewed thee in the mount.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Ex. 26:30; 1\u00a0Ne. 17:8 (7\u201314); Ether 2:16.",
                        "start": 41,
                        "end": 48
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 24,
                        "end": 28
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}